# sample.swc -- a tiny synthetic neuron for demos and tests.
# Columns: n  structure  x  y  z  radius  parent
# structure ids: 1=soma, 2=axon, 3=basal dendrite, 4=apical dendrite
#
# soma (3 points)
1 1 0.0 0.0 0.0 2.0 -1
2 1 0.0 1.0 0.0 2.0 1
3 1 0.0 -1.0 0.0 2.0 1
# apical dendrite going up, branching into two tips
4 4 0.0 3.0 0.0 1.0 2
5 4 0.0 6.0 0.0 0.8 4
6 4 0.0 9.0 0.0 0.6 5
7 4 -3.0 12.0 0.0 0.4 6
8 4 -5.0 15.0 0.0 0.3 7
9 4 3.0 12.0 0.0 0.4 6
10 4 5.0 15.0 0.0 0.3 9
# basal dendrite going down, branching
11 3 0.0 -3.0 0.0 1.0 3
12 3 -3.0 -6.0 0.0 0.7 11
13 3 -6.0 -8.0 0.0 0.5 12
14 3 3.0 -6.0 0.0 0.7 11
15 3 6.0 -8.0 0.0 0.5 14
# axon going out along +x
16 2 2.0 0.0 0.0 0.6 1
17 2 6.0 0.0 1.0 0.5 16
18 2 10.0 0.0 2.0 0.4 17
19 2 14.0 0.0 3.0 0.3 18
